Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:26.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}V 1. dni na svete, pod stromom života,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:32.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}dvaja z nás počuli hlasy veľrýb, odrážajúce sa z diaľky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:39.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}So všetkým, čo sme stratili a všetko, čo sme milovali,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:45.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}čo sme mali v náručí, kam sa to zatúľalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:52.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Odpoveď leží v jantári slnka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:58.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Ak by som ťa nestretla, zničila by som anjela.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.39,0:02:04.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Moja duša posadnutá okamihom nesmrteľnosti,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:07.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}nezraní moje krídla.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.74,0:02:14.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Zrodila som sa, aby som spoznala tento pocit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:20.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po 1.000 rokov a ešte ďalších 2.000, som ťa ľúbila.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:27.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po 8.000 rokoch, som ťa ľúbila ešte viac.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:33.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po ďalších 100.000.000 rokov a ešte ďalších 2.000, ťa budem stále ľúbiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:41.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Od 1. dňa, keď som ťa spoznala, hudba v mojom pekle nikdy neprestala.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:57.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1500)\pos(187,257)}"Čas jantára"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to zložené z 80% z uhlíku,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:57.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a 10% organickej zlúčeniny tvorí kyslík.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:59.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Inými slovami, jantár.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:03.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je dokázané, že je vo vnútri pierko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:06.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veríme, že sa jantár vytvoril okolo pierka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:10.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovoríš, že to patrilo dinosaurovi s krídlami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dáta sú príliš vzdialené.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:19.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhlík, ktorý tvorí jantár je približne z pred 12.000 rokov.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:24.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,12.000 rokov?! Jantár je skamenená živica stromov!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:27.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,V tom čase sa to nemohlo vytvoriť.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:29.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Určite si sa neprepočítala?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:35.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jediné pierko uzamknuté v jantári...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:41.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Musí sa to doručiť Slnečnému Krídlu, aby sme vyhrali vojnu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:47.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitola 6, verš 4, "Mysteriózna pieseň" zo Svätej knihy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:52.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môže to zmeniť celú vojnu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že si povedal, že to bolo "prepočítanie"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:04:02.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak to má niečo spoločné s Ťieňovými Anjelmi, tak to musíme analyzovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:07.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Musíme brať želania z pred 12.000 rokov vážne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to náš drahocenný deň voľna.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:39.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Budeš tu čupieť celý deň?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:41.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:44.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,No, áno, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:47.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne chcem byť povýšený...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako sa ti darí na konci semestra?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:50.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizerne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:59.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz hrajú balet "Giselle." Chceš ísť?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:06.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Giselle je príbeh o úbohej žene, ktorá bola využitá sebeckosťou...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To zabije zábavu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:11.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabije? To je moje nešťastie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, Reika, vôbec nie si taká.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:22.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď si so mnou, tak ťa stretne nešťastie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:27.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak mi dovolíš, zahalím ťa do môjho srdca!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:39.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo by si chcel na narodeniny?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Moje narodeniny? To je ešte ďaleko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:46.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A čo toto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mohla by to byť kadidelnica?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:56.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nosili ženy pod sukňami v 18. storočí.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:00.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:02.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,čo toto?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:09.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpusť mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:12.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Odišiel si zo stráže!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:21.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo! Prestaň! Nie tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:24.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal, že nikdy neodíde zo stráže!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:28.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat! Takýchto chlapov by si nemal brať tak vážne!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:30.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pravda, bolo to detinské.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:32.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som aspoň čiastočne dospelý!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vidíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:55.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Generátor bariéry... Je to najkrajšia vec!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:59.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Má rovnaký základ, ako v iných mestách,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale vonkajšok je oveľa silnejší.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:04.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vedel si to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:07.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Generátor bariéry závisí na geologických vrstvách.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:11.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu, tu je najsilnejší.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:14.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto bolo toto miesto vybrané ako základňa pre Deavu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:16.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach, tak si vedel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:17.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prirodzene!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:22.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:51.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Títo bezkrídlí bastardi. Zničili pečať?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:59.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovoríš, že naše pierko padlo do rúk bezkrídlych?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:02.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne, pán Johannes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:05.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké nádeje sú ukryté v pierku?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je záznam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:10.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Avšak, je z Atlandie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:15.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Predpovedáme, že obsahuje dôležité informácie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:18.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pán Johannes, daj nám povolenie, aby sme ho získali späť.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:24.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môže to byť pasca, aby nás vylákali von.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:29.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma, chcel si vbehnúť do hniezda Slnečného Krídla?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:34.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Moroha, tak necháš bezkrídlych...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:37.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...aby sa dotýkali ich špinavými rukami nášho pierka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:44.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To Moroha nemyslel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:49.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,V žiadnom prípade by nemali pošpiniť, čo je naše.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:52.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale keď je na takom hnusnom mieste ako je Deava,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:55.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,tak ako sa dostaneme cez bariéru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:58.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám plán.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:15.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepočuješ to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Strom života...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:23.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spomínaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:25.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne pred tebou...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:32.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Strom života... Stvorenie sveta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:35.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rena!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zavolaj lekársky tím!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:38.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:41.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:43.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Účinky na ľudské telo sú neznáme.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Taká neskúsenosť...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:48.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci pozor:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:52.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hocikto, kto sa dotkne pierka, bude prísne potrestaný.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:53.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:56.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Žiadne otázky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:03.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:07.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat! Deje sa niečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:08.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevstupuj!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepribližuj sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:23.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nesmieš sa ku mne priblížiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:25.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Niečo hrozné...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:38.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepribližuj sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:40.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:51.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie si sama sebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:56.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vážne, nie si sama sebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:58.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Obyčajne by si mi dala facku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:00.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoja sila amazonky je všetko, čo máš.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:07.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:12.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Blázon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:15.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To si už viac ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechceš vidieť to pierko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:32.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Fudo povedal nie,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:35.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,ale nechceš ho preto vidieť ešte viac?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:41.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môže tam byť niečo o Baronovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:45.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron, Baron... stále iba Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:51.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to jediná osoba, ktorú môžem volať priateľom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:16.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ovocie chutí najlepšie predtým, než úplne dozrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:17.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:21.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sme pripravení na útok.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:27.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Musíš si želať, aby si ho znova stretol... tvojho drahého priateľa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:34.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja sa chcem tiež s niekým, pre mňa vzácnym, stretnúť.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veľmi vzácnym.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:51.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedala si niekomu, že ho ľúbiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:57.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A vy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:58.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:00.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpustite mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:20.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje pocity sú rozpustené v čaji, ktorý nechce byť vypitý.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:30.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ženy budú vždy niečo, čomu nebudeme schopný porozumieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:39.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Len myši. Necháme ich tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:26.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkať.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Niečo tu cítim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:35.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Cítiš ióny infračerveného lúču?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:39.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ióny? Čo to je? Iba poznám ich pach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:14.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Už som to niekedy cítil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:15.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:16.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel som si spomenúť.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo! Vzchop sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:35.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeden so zastrihnutými krídlami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:07.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten deň...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:10.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Volala som tvoje meno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:13.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:15.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...som volal tvoje.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:23.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:24.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Seliane...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:33.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by som ťa nestretla...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:37.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by sme sa nikdy nestretli...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:41.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by sme sa nestretli, mohla si ostať zabijakom anjelov.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:06.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nešťastné stretnutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:08.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A šťastné stretnutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:13.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Seliane...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:16.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:33.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zamiloval som sa do teba... človek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:39.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zamilovala som sa do teba... Ťieňový Anjel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:53.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:01.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mal som ťa popraviť.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:06.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak ma zabi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:08.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:26.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius, priviedol som hlúpeho bezkrídleho, ktorý ťa chcel zachrániť.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:27.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Seliane!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:30.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:37.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preklínaj svoju vlastnú bezmocnosť, aby si zachránila život toho, koho ľúbiš.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zastav to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:48.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak ušetrím bezkrídleho, tak sa ku mne vrátiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:11.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Moroha, myslíš, že necháš jej život v mojich rukách?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:14.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebudem prosiť o svoj život Ťieňového Anjela!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:18.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak tu máš, čo si si vybrala!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:30.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:34.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak veľmi ju ľúbiš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:36.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak veľmi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:42.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A potom, sme bojovali...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:44.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spolu sme bojovali proti Ťieňovým Anjelom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:00.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Seliane...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:03.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:26.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to? To je hnus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:28.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,No, u mňa je to rovnaké!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:38.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spomínaš si, čo sa stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:41.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Len matne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,V našich minulých životoch, sme my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:51.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepriateľský útok! Všetci elementi hláste sa na Veliteľstve!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:03.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prišiel som ťa pozrieť,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:05.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Slnečné Krídlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:40.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia! Pierre!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:43.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohnivá päsť!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:49.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Z 12.000 rokov utrpenia prichádza tiché znamenie skazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.87,0:23:55.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nabudúce v Aquarionovi: "12.000 rokov starý ľúbostný list"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:24:00.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(20,0)\pos(311,228)}"Cesta snov"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:23:57.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je taký pekný...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.77,0:23:59.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,
